	<h1 class="title">「酸汤鱼经济学」纳什的问题出在哪了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3891/small/3891.jpg?1418027288" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">酸汤鱼 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-29 10:18:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10174/medium/10174.jpg?1436651149" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="10174" data-title="《「酸汤鱼经济学」纳什的问题出在哪了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10174/medium/10174.jpg?1436651149" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10174.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
